"},{"pid":"63f78a3e640910bff5badf8446c39be652e4bd8a","tid":652633,"uid":84272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T04:12:41.000Z","msg":"我打橫生，果排食得多熱氣野又夜訓就會發炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個牙醫都叫我mok<br />\n但真心貴<br />\nMok左1隻<br />\n其餘3隻要開刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 起碼3000起跳"},{"pid":"93a09009433e3298fe419dc6c29b8bf0324c037d","tid":652633,"uid":60686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63f78a3e640910bff5badf8446c39be652e4bd8a","tid":652633,"uid":84272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T04:12:41.000Z","msg":"我打橫生，果排食得多熱氣野又夜訓就會發炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個牙醫都叫我mok<br />\n但真心貴<br />\nMok左1隻<br />\n其餘3隻要開刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 起碼3000起跳"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T04:20:16.000Z","msg":"個陣mok 有冇打針？<br />\n聽講打針好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90ddad15a36aa4376f8c6853524f37416c7159a5","tid":652633,"uid":6425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93a09009433e3298fe419dc6c29b8bf0324c037d","tid":652633,"uid":60686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63f78a3e640910bff5badf8446c39be652e4bd8a","tid":652633,"uid":84272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T04:12:41.000Z","msg":"我打橫生，果排食得多熱氣野又夜訓就會發炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個牙醫都叫我mok<br />\n但真心貴<br />\nMok左1隻<br />\n其餘3隻要開刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 起碼3000起跳"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T04:20:16.000Z","msg":"個陣mok 有冇打針？<br />\n聽講打針好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T04:51:20.000Z","msg":"我果時預先俾左粒止痛藥食<br />\n打針都唔太痛<br />\n係做做下feel到痛，即係舉手同佢講，補多兩針<br />\n<br />\n有得剝就快啲剝啦<br />\n唔係遲啲爛埋隔離果啲牙仲麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\